reviewText: I have not witnessed the films......I purchased them for my junior high nieces term paper.....she got good grade
I loved this video, thought my students would hate it...but they LOVE it!  Great insight into the "between the scenes" by the Staff that actually run the People's House.
Very informative as to who "really" runs the White House - and it's not the Presidential family!  Also, cool behind the scenes information.
